<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>Kum A Sawt Um Ngeilo</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Chung van gamah ka In guotsa um,
 Ana ngaihtuoh di'n Lalpa chieh ta;
 Hukdamna gam nuom achun,
 Hukdamsa hehpihte tawh,
 Lawi khawma chawihat la sa zing ta ding.

[V2]
 Kum a sawt um ngeilo,
 Kipahna gam achun;
 Gim genthei um talo,
 Zie mun achun va cheng ding i hiu.

[V3]
 2. Kei dingin Hukdampa hungthi ta,
 Ka thagau hukdam na ding ziekin,
 Gitloh a dim sietlei ah,
 Kei apata peldawk di'n,
 Van gam nuom hawihtak a cheng zing dingin.

[V4]
 3. Phat tampi chieh zing ding Aw Lalpa,
 Keimah nei vawp zing ie tih ka he'n;
 Mang lo hielin I Lalpa'n,
 I chenkhawmna diu lim ah,
 Etnawp etdah umlo chamna leng ta.

[V5]
 4. Chung van gam sana khawpi a chun,
 Kah leh mau, gim theihna um ta lo;
 Nunnawp zaila sa zing ding,
 Chawl-le-nan beisuok ta ding,
 Nunnuom zing ding chung gam In nuom a chun.</lyrics>
<hymn_number>308</hymn_number>
</song>